data.description: Welcome to the canvas for your renovation dreams! This 2-bedroom, 1-bath home sits on a sprawling 1 plus acre lot in the much desired Armuchee area. This property holds tremendous potential for those seeking to create their ideal homestead.  Key features of this home include a brand new heat and air conditioning system, a large covered parking area to protect your vehicles from the elements, a small outbuilding for additional storage, and a 1 plus acre lot with approximately 640 feet of road frontage.  This property is the perfect opportunity for those with a vision and the desire to transform a property into their dream home. The expansive lot allows for plenty of outdoor space, gardening, or potential expansion. With a brand new heating and air unit, you've already taken a significant step toward creating a comfortable living environment. If you're ready to roll up your sleeves and create a space that truly reflects your style, this property is the perfect starting point. The potential is limited only by your imagination.
